HEADWORD: Somewhither
<hw>Some"whith`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>To some
indeterminate place; to some place or other.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Driven by the winds of temptation <qex>somewhither</qex>.</q>
